K10D0104_H0107:442b-1: a'arya ta th'a ga t'a n'a ma buddha kshe tra gu nokta dharma parya ya /
K10D0104_H0107:442b-3: 'phags pa de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi sangs rgyas
K10D0104_H0107:442b-4: kyi zhing gi yon tan brjod pa'i chos kyi rnam
K10D0104_H0107:442b-5: grangs / sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
K10D0104_H0107:442b-6: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa dus gcig na /
K10D0104_H0107:442b-7: bcom ldan 'das yul mnyam dka' na chos kyi dgon
K10D0104_H0107:442b-8: pa byang chub kyi snying po na nor bu rdo
K10D0104_H0107:442b-9: rjes spras pa'i padma'i snying po'i sengge'i khri la bzhugs
K10D0104_H0107:442b-10: te / byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun chen po
K10D0104_H0107:442b-11: sangs rgyas kyi zhing brjod du med pa bye ba
K10D0104_H0107:442b-12: khrag khrig brgya stong phrag bcu'i rdul phra rab snyed
K10D0104_H0107:442b-13: kyi byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po dang
K10D0104_H0107:442b-14: te / thabs cig go / de'i tshe byang chub
K10D0104_H0107:442b-15: sems dpa'i 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor 'dus pa de nyid
K10D0104_H0107:442b-16: du byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'od
K10D0104_H0107:442b-17: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rgyal po zhes bya ba
K10D0104_H0107:442b-19: de nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po
K10D0104_H0107:442b-20: 'od bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rgyal po sangs rgyas
K10D0104_H0107:442b-21: kyi mthus stan las langs te /
K10D0104_H0107:442b-22: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs thams cad la smras pa /
K10D0104_H0107:443a-1: gyi khams mi mjed kyi bskal pa de ni /
K10D0104_H0107:443a-2: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa 'od dpag med
K10D0104_H0107:443a-3: kyi sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'jig rten gyi khams bde
K10D0104_H0107:443a-4: ba can gyi nyin zhag gcig go /
K10D0104_H0107:443a-6: gang 'jig rten gyi khams bde ba can gyi bskal pa de ni /
K10D0104_H0107:443a-7: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa mi 'khrugs pa'i
K10D0104_H0107:443a-8: sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'jig rten gyi khams mngon par
K10D0104_H0107:443a-9: dga' ba'i nyin zhag gcig go /
K10D0104_H0107:443a-11: gang 'jig rten gyi khams mngon par dga' ba'i bskal pa de ni /
K10D0104_H0107:443a-12: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa rdo rje snying
K10D0104_H0107:443a-13: pos rab tu 'dul ba'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'jig
K10D0104_H0107:443a-14: rten gyi khams ngur smrig gi rgyal mtshan gyi nyin
K10D0104_H0107:443a-15: zhag gcig go / kye rgyal ba'i sras dag /
K10D0104_H0107:443a-16: gang 'jig rten gyi khams dur smrig gi rgyal mtshan gyi bskal pa de ni /
K10D0104_H0107:443a-17: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa shin tu rnam
K10D0104_H0107:443a-18: par gdon mi za bar padmo rab tu rgyas pa'i
K10D0104_H0107:443a-19: sku'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'jig rten gyi khams phyir
K10D0104_H0107:443a-20: mi ldog pa'i 'khor lo dbyangs kyi nyin zhag gcig
K10D0104_H0107:443a-21: go / kye rgyal ba'i sras dag /
K10D0104_H0107:443a-22: gang 'jig rten gyi khams phyir mi ldog pa'i 'khor lo dbyangs kyi bskal pa de ni /
K10D0104_H0107:443a-23: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa chos kyi rgyal
K10D0104_H0107:443a-24: mtshan gyi zhing 'jig rten gyi khams rdul dang bral
K10D0104_H0107:443a-27: gang 'jig rten gyi khams rdul dang bral ba'i bskal pa de ni /
K10D0104_H0107:443b-0: bcom @443b ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa sengge'i sangs
K10D0104_H0107:443b-1: rgyas kyi zhing 'jig rten gyi khams mar me ldan
K10D0104_H0107:443b-4: gang 'jig rten gyi khams mar me ldan gyi bskal
K10D0104_H0107:443b-5: pa de ni; bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa
K10D0104_H0107:443b-6: rnam par snang mdzad kyi sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'jig
K10D0104_H0107:443b-7: rten gyi khams 'od bzang po'i nyin zhag gcig go
K10D0104_H0107:443b-9: gang 'jig rten gyi khams 'od bzang po'i bskal pa de ni /
K10D0104_H0107:443b-10: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa chos kyi 'od
K10D0104_H0107:443b-11: zer rab tu rgyas pa'i sku'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing
K10D0104_H0107:443b-12: 'jig rten gyi khams 'da' bar dka' ba'i nyin zhag
K10D0104_H0107:443b-13: gcig go / kye rgyal ba'i sras dag /
K10D0104_H0107:443b-14: gang 'jig rten gyi khams 'da' bar dka' ba'i bskal pa de ni /
K10D0104_H0107:443b-15: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa mngon par shes
K10D0104_H0107:443b-16: pa thams cad blo gros 'od zer rgyal po'i sangs
K10D0104_H0107:443b-17: rgyas kyi zhing 'jig rten gyi khams rnam par brgyan
K10D0104_H0107:443b-20: gang 'jig rten gyi khams rnam par brgyan gyi bskal pa de ni /
K10D0104_H0107:443b-21: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa zla ba'i thugs
K10D0104_H0107:443b-22: kyi sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'jig rten gyi khams me
K10D0104_H0107:443b-23: long gi dkyil 'khor dbyangs kyi nyin zhag gcig go
K10D0104_H0107:443b-25: gang 'jig rten gyi khams brtag cing bgrang ba la
K10D0104_H0107:443b-26: 'jug pa'i tshul 'dis sangs rgyas kyi zhing brgya stong
K10D0104_H0107:443b-27: phrag bcur tshang ba'i rdul phra rab snyed 'das pa'i
K10D0104_H0107:443b-28: pha rol na bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa
K10D0104_H0107:444a-2: rigs kyi bu mo la la zhig de bzhin gshegs
K10D0104_H0107:444a-3: pa rnams kyi sangs rgyas kyi zhing gi yon tan
K10D0104_H0107:444a-4: brjod pa'i chos kyi rnam grangs 'di 'chang ngam /
K10D0104_H0107:444a-8: gzhan dag la'ang rgya cher yang dag par rab tu ston na /
K10D0104_H0107:444a-9: de 'chi ba'i dus kyi tshe phyogs bcu mtha' yas
K10D0104_H0107:444a-10: pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing rgya mtsho rab 'byams dag
K10D0104_H0107:444a-11: gi sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams de'i mdun na
K10D0104_H0107:444a-13: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang
K10D0104_H0107:444a-14: chub mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas kyi bar du
K10D0104_H0107:444a-16: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis gnang ste /
K10D0104_H0107:444a-17: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'od bsam
K10D0104_H0107:444a-18: gyis mi khyab pa'i rgyal po dga' zhing de skad
K10D0104_H0107:444a-19: ces smras so // byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa'

K10D0104_H0107:444a-21: sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'od bsam gyis mi

K10D0104_H0107:444a-23: ces smras so // do // 'phags pa de bzhin
K10D0104_H0107:444b-0: @444b gshegs pa rnams kyi sangs rgyas kyi zhing gi
